Privacy Policy for StoryFont
Effective Date: 01 Jan 2025
Welcome to StoryFont, the font styling application developed by Alireza Namazian. Protecting your privacy is our priority, and this Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information while you use the app. By downloading, accessing, or using StoryFont, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Please read it carefully to understand your rights and our practices.
1. Information We Collect
a. Information You Provide Directly
Email Address: If provided, we may use it for support and communication.
b. Automatically Collected Data
When you use StoryFont, we may collect the following:
User Region: To optimize language and content settings.
Usage Data: Includes app interactions, session duration, and feature usage.
Device Data: Such as IP address, device model, operating system, and browser type.
Crash and Performance Data: Collected using trusted third-party tools like Google Analytics, Firebase, and Metabase to diagnose issues and improve app functionality.
c. Cookies and Similar Technologies
We use analytics tools that may store cookies or similar tracking mechanisms to enhance the app experience. These expire after your session ends and do not track you beyond app usage.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the data collected to:
Improve app performance and troubleshoot technical issues.
Enhance security and develop new features.
Personalize user experience within the app.
We do not share user data with third parties for advertising or analytics purposes.
3. Data Storage and Retention
All collected data is stored securely and retained for up to one year after each session.
After this period, data is automatically deleted unless legally required to be retained.
4. Data Security
We take the following measures to protect your information:
Encryption: Industry-standard encryption secures data during transmission.
Secure Storage: Data is stored on protected servers with limited access.
Retention Limits: Data is deleted within the defined retention period unless required otherwise.
While we strive to maintain the highest security standards, no system is completely foolproof.
5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
StoryFont is safe for users of all ages and does not have age restrictions. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have collected data from a child, please contact us to request its deletion.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to:
Access and Portability: Request a copy of your personal data.
Rectification: Correct any inaccurate data.
Deletion: Request deletion of your personal data.
Withdraw Consent: Withdraw consent for data processing at any time.
To exercise these rights, contact us at
info@creativebug.app
.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted within the app and on our website. Continued use of the app after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email:
